OL,3,CResidents evacuated from homes after
OL,4,C'suspect package' found
OL,6,FResidents on two streets in Llanelli
OL,7,Fhave been evacuated from their homes
OL,8,Fafter a suspect package was found.
OL,10,FDyfed Powys Police say they are
OL,11,Fcurrently dealing with an incident on
OL,12,FLong Row and Adulam Row Felinfoel,
OL,13,FLlanelli.
OL,15,FThey add that the area remains closed
OL,16,Fwhile it waits for a specialist
OL,17,Fexplosive ordnance disposal team to
OL,18,Farrive and examine the item.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
