OL,3,CResidents evacuated from homes after
OL,4,C'suspect package' found
OL,6,FBoth roads have been closed to traffic
OL,7,Fwith residents asked to leave their
OL,8,Fhomes.
OL,10,FIn a statement the force has said: "We
OL,11,Fare currently dealing with an incident
OL,12,Fin Long Row, Felinfoel, Llanelli,
OL,13,Ffollowing a report of a suspect
OL,14,Fpackage being found at 12.25pm.
OL,16,F"Officers, along with Mid and West
OL,17,FWales Fire and Rescue Service and the
OL,18,FWelsh Ambulance Service, were
OL,19,Fdispatched to the scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
