OL,3,CResidents evacuated from homes after
OL,4,C'suspect package' found
OL,6,FLong Row and Adulam Row are closed to
OL,7,Ftraffic, and people living in both
OL,8,Fstreets have been asked to leave their
OL,9,Fhomes as a precaution while the
OL,10,Fpackage is examined."
